<class module="bajaui" runtimeProfile="wb" qualifiedName="javax.baja.ui.options.OptionsManager" name="OptionsManager" packageName="javax.baja.ui.options" public="true" interface="true" abstract="true" category="interface">
<description>
OptionsManager is used to manage BOptions for a the &#xa; current user.  Access to the OptionsManager is via &#xa; &lt;code&gt;BWidget.getApplication().getOptionsManager()&lt;/code&gt; or&#xa; &lt;code&gt;BOptions.getOptionsManager()&lt;/code&gt;.
</description>
